---
# v1.0.5.3 §1.3 — This file is embedded into the server bundle at build time
# (esbuild `?raw` import in src/prompts/loader.ts) and used as the first-run
# USER.md seed in the platform AppData directory.
#
# To change the default profile that new users see:
#   1. Edit this file
#   2. Run `pnpm build` (rebuilds the bundle with the new content)
#   3. New installs will seed from the updated content
#
# This file is NOT used at runtime in dev mode (where a manually-edited
# prompts/USER.md can take precedence) — it's only the fallback when the
# AppData USER.md doesn't exist yet.
name: Sample Student
age: 13
level: intermediate
goals:
  - Improve daily English conversation
  - Build vocabulary for school subjects
  - Get comfortable speaking aloud
interests:
  - Basketball
  - Video games (Minecraft, Roblox)
  - Anime
  - Pizza and burgers
voice_accent: en-US
voice_speed: 1.0
---

# STUDENT

Sample student is a 13-year-old Chinese middle schooler. They are shy at first
but warm up after a few minutes. They know basic English grammar but rarely
speak it. They respond well to short, fun questions about their interests.
